reviewText: We love edgy humor, and this series fits that bill perfectly.  Truly one of the funniest shows ever for us.  We can watch some of these every day and they just get funnier each time.  If you like The Boondocks or South Park, you would probably enjoy this series.  Player Hater's Ball and the Charlie Murphy stories alone make this a worthwhile purchase, but you get much more than that!
